==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tache
<hw>Tache</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Tack</er> a
kind of nail.]</ety> <def>Something used for taking hold or holding; a
catch; a loop; a button.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Ex. xxvi.
6.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tache</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tache
<hw>Tache</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>tache</ets> spot. See
<er>Techy</er>.]</ety> <def>A spot, stain, or blemish.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Warner.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tachhydrite</ent>⟦br⟧
